race.comment: BANG STICK (1) is a consistent conveyance who has hit the top-five in all nine career outings and is yet to put in a poor one. Will be ready to peak now third-up from the spell and looks the one they all have to run down. VALUBIOUS (6) finally shed the maiden tag last time out and will have derived a stack of confidence from that breakthrough victory. Genuine top-three prospects. NORDIC INVADER (4) is one from one around this circuit and only needs some luck navigating from the sticky draw to be playing a major role in the outcome. ASPEN COWBOY (3) has put back-to-back wins together since joining the new stable and can make his presence felt again. CHANCE (8) is still a maiden but hasn't been too far away of late and may earn some minor money.
